parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the liftgate latch can cause the rear hatch to open while in motion, leading to accidents, injuries, and damage to the vehicle.
symptoms: The rear hatch is difficult to close
the rear hatch will not latch from time to time
the rear hatch opens while in motion
the rear hatch comes open upon being rear-ended.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the manual window handles can cause entrapment in an emergency exit situation, potentially leading to serious injury or fatalities.
symptoms: making it difficult or impossible to open or close the window.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the remote entry system can cause inconvenience and potentially lead to safety issues if the doors do not shut properly.
symptoms: The remote entry system no longer functions
and the doors may not shut properly.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The difficulty in closing the sliding door can cause inconvenience and potentially lead to safety issues if the door does not shut properly.
symptoms: The sliding door requires extra effort to close

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the hydraulic cylinder lift struts can cause unexpected descent of the liftgate, potentially leading to injury or damage.
symptoms: The hydraulic cylinder lift struts fail
causing the liftgate to descend unexpectedly without warning.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The transmission slipping or failure can cause the vehicle to move unexpectedly, leading to accidents, damage to the vehicle, or injury to occupants or bystanders.
symptoms: The transmission slips out of gear
the transmission makes unusual noises or vibrations.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the seatback can cause serious injury or fatalities to occupants, especially children, in the event of a rear-impact collision.
symptoms: The seatback collapses or reclines backward during a rear-impact collision
potentially causing injury or ejection of occupants.
